<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī śakavarṣamulu 1094 nēṁṭṭi yuttarā 
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yana saṁkrāṁtti nimittamuna paṁḍḍanāyaka sōma 
<lb n="3" break="no"/>na peggaḍa kōḍku maṁḍḍana tamatallidaṁḍrulaku dha(sa)mma 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>tamugā śrī sōmēśvara mahādēvara bhōgarāgamulaku 
<lb n="5"/>peṭṭina vṛttulu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 
</p>

